kobuki_control########

PREREQUISITES:
Install kobukidrivers


Build, Setup & Run:

cd ~/final-project-flysky/qbot_ws
colcon build --packages-select kobuki_control --symlink-install
source install/setup.bash
ros2 run kobuki_control kobuki_control_node





Publish commands (in a seperate terminal):

**Source the workspace**

Forward:
ros2 topic pub /cmd_vel geometry_msgs/msg/Twist "{linear: {x: 0.10}, angular: {z: 0.0}}"


Spin: (Left)
ros2 topic pub /cmd_vel geometry_msgs/msg/Twist "{linear: {x: 0.0}, angular: {z: 0.5}}"

Curve:
ros2 topic pub /cmd_vel geometry_msgs/msg/Twist "{linear: {x: 0.10}, angular: {z: 0.30}}"

Stop:
ros2 topic pub --once /cmd_vel geometry_msgs/msg/Twist "{linear: {x: 0.0}, angular: {z: 0.0}}"


OBSERVE OUTPUT MESSAGES PRINTED ON Kobuki_control running terminal